# Stage 08 Root Stderr Summary

Key stderr/log excerpts are preserved in the detailed evidence files:

- `asan_build/default_configure_stderr.log`: GCC toolset 14 sanitizer configure fails with missing `libasan_preinit.o` and `-lasan`.
- `asan_build/workaround_configure_stderr.log`: same GCC sanitizer-runtime failure after the Stage 05 `-include climits` workaround.
- `asan_gtest/bloom_test_target_stderr.log`: `gmake: *** No rule to make target 'bloom_test'. Stop.`
- `asan_tcl/module_load_no_preload_redis.log`: Redis module load fails with undefined `__asan_option_detect_stack_use_after_return`.
- `asan_tcl/module_load_gcc11_preload_stderr.log`: `LD_PRELOAD` rejects the GCC 11 sanitizer linker-script files as "file too short".
- `asan_tcl/runtime_discovery.log`: runtime search found only linker-script placeholders, no loadable ASAN/UBSAN dynamic runtime.

No sanitizer or UBSAN stack trace from `modules/gemini-bloom` was produced because the sanitizer runtime could not be loaded for Redis integration, and no sanitizer GTest executable was available.

